#### Model diagnostics

Checking the health of the machine.

*   **[Coefficient of determination](/Coefficient_of_determination):** A statistical measure of how well the regression predictions approximate the real data points.
*   **[Confusion matrix](/Confusion_matrix):** A table summarizing classification results. Shows where the model got confused. It always gets confused.
*   **[Learning curve](/Learning_curve_(machine_learning)):** Plotting performance against training data size. Shows if it's learning, or just memorizing.
*   **[ROC curve (Receiver Operating Characteristic)](/Receiver_operating_characteristic):** A plot showing the diagnostic ability of a binary classifier system.

